This paper is primarily focused on a novel distributed relational database system, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the challenges of running SQL on Big Data platforms, which could be categorized under distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the system's tailored execution framework, which could be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG).
